name: amp_blank
doc:
Operates amplifier blanking. 
i = 0 = not blanked, 1 = blanked

name: in_coupling
doc:
Sets dynamic reserve. 
i = 0 = low noise, 1 = high DR, 
2 = calibration gains (defaults).

name: listen_all
doc:
Listen all. Makes all attached 
SR560’s listeners.

name: listen
doc:
Listen command. Makes 
SR560 with address i (0,1,2,3) 
a listener.

name: lo_filter_freq
doc:
Sets lowpass filter frequency. 
i = 0 – 15 sets frequency 
= 0.03 Hz to 1 MHz.

name: res_overload
doc: Reset overload for half a second.

name: ver_gain
doc:
Sets the vernier gain status. 
i = 0 = cal’d gain, 
1 = vernier gain.

name: ver_gain_set
doc:
Sets the vernier gain to i %. 
i = 0 to 100.
